snippet.title: FragPunk | Closed Beta Preview - Coming Oct 10!
snippet.description:
Get ready for the thrill of FragPunk's Closed Beta! 🎮 Dive into the action with new Lancers, shard cards, and an exhilarating game mode. The battlefield is set for an epic upgrade—are you prepared to join the fight? Don't miss the preview of what you can expect in the upcoming closed beta on 22:00, October 10th (UTC+0)!

Don't miss out! Secure your spot in the #FragPunkCBT now:

👉 Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2943650/FragPunk
👉 Xbox: Join via Xbox Insider Hub

Stay on top of the latest news and updates by following us on our socials:

🔗 Official Website: https://www.fragpunk.com/
🔗 X: https://x.com/intent/follow?screen_name=PlayFragPunk
🔗 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PlayFragPunk
🔗 TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@playfragpunk
🔗 Discord: https://discord.gg/fragpunk
🔗 Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/PlayFragPunk/

📣 Don't forget to like, comment, and subscribe for more updates. Hit that notification bell so you never miss an update from #FragPunk!
